스킹","body":"그렇다 해도 치게 되는 속도가 엄청 빠르잖아.\n제대로 잔 거야?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event150-03-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"괜찮아. 평소보다 연습 시간은 늘었지만.\n그런데 라이브 일정을 고려해보면 이 페이스로 해도 늦을 정도야.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event150-03-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"오늘이 화요일이니까 라이브까지는 앞으로……\n아!","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":31,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":31,"voiceId":"event150-03-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":33}],"windowDisplayName":"마스킹","body":"뭐야, 왜 그래!?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":33,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":33,"voiceId":"event150-03-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":31}],"windowDisplayName":"레이야","body":"숙제 기간이 내일까지인 걸 까먹고 있었어.\n어쩌